U.K. Football Clubs Owe 22 Million Pounds Taxes, Telegraph Says

-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 
2011-03-27T09:03:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-27/u-k-football-clubs-owe-22-million-pounds-taxes-telegraph-says.html
The U.K Treasury was owed about 22
million pounds ($35 million) by football clubs at the end of the
April last year, the  Sunday Telegraph  reported, citing
government figures.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rachel Graham in London 
